- For four, check if options include "D: kite", "H: rectangle", or other quadrilaterals, and inspect side relationships before choosing.
- For ambiguous four-sided figures, symmetry and side pairing must be used (if present) to differentiate between "kite", "rectangle", or "trapezoid" as labeled in options.

