   - *Circle*: Usually indicated by large smooth curves; in SVG, this is often rendered with 'A' (arc) commands spanning a full 360°, or 'C'/'Q' (cubic/quadratic Bezier) arranged circularly. Do NOT confuse ellipses for circles; circles require equal radii.
