- Never output intermediary working or partial answers—output is solely a `####` line with the answer.
- Focus on precise intent and factual content, not superficial cues or keyword matching.
- Where tasks could allow multiple groupings or edge cases, default to explicit mathematical or contextually dominant standards; never guess or summarize.

