- Do NOT assume that reallocated funds (such as money transferred to a debit card or savings) have been spent, unless the question specifies.
- When considering "remaining money" or similar, include all unspent amounts, regardless of where they are kept (cash, card, etc.), unless the problem directs otherwise.
