- `<path d="M 30,10 L 50,60 L 10,60 Z"/>` with options including (J) triangle should produce output: J
- `<path d="M 10,10 L 40,10 L 40,40 L 10,40 Z"/>` with (H) rectangle, (D) kite: output H
